{
  "info": {
    "name": "MDR - BIOFUND API",
    "_postman_id": "mdr-biofund-api-collection",
    "description": "Coleção completa para testar a API do sistema MDR (Mecanismo de Denúncia e Reclamação).\n\nBase URL: http://localhost/facul.php/biofund_api/public/api\n\nFluxo recomendado:\n1. Fazer login numa das pastas Auth\n2. O token é guardado automaticamente na variável {{token}}\n3. Usar os restantes endpoints\n\nUtilizadores de teste:\n- Admin:       admin@mdr.biofund.org.mz / Admin@MDR2024\n- Gestor Maputo: gestor@mdr.biofund.org.mz / 12345678  (sem urgente, com GBV)\n- Gestor Gaza:   Gaza@mdr.biofund.org.mz   / 12345678  (com urgente e GBV)\n- Funcionário:   funcionario@mdr.biofund.org.mz / 12345678",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost/facul.php/biofund_api/public/api",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "occurrence_id",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "tracking_code",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "attachment_id",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "Login - Admin",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.token);",
                  "    console.log('Token guardado:', res.token.substring(0, 20) + '...');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@mdr.biofund.org.mz\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@MDR2024\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Admin - acesso total a todas as ocorrências e utilizadores.\nreceives_urgent_alerts: true | receives_gbv_alerts: true"
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Login - Gestor Maputo (sem urgente)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
